  "description": "Synthetic V&V 40 UnitOfAssurance for CFD-based hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. Validation evidence leverages the Heck et al. in vitro hemolysis dataset as an external comparator, with mesh convergence and solver verification provided. Assessment concludes all seven assessed factors meet the required MRL 2 gradations.",
